name: Team Kaylie
overview: After a brush with the law, teen celebrity Kaylie Konrad swaps social stardom for court-ordered chaos as a middle school wilderness club leader.

seasons.name: Part 1
seasons.overview: After a brush with the law, teenage celebrity billionaire Kaylie Konrad is court-ordered to lead an inner-city wilderness club.

seasons.name: Part 2
seasons.overview: Ready for more glitz, glam and grit? Kaylie and the Porcupines sharpen their skills for a new slate of action-packed shenanigans.

episodes.name: Be-wilderness
episodes.overview: While the Pico Porcupines prepare for a new year of outdoor adventures, Kaylie ditches her luxury life and learns the ropes of her rugged assignment.

episodes.name: Invasion of the Lumberjerks
episodes.overview: The Porcupines brace for bad energy as they host the Lumberjacks for a campsite competition. Meanwhile, Principal Dana puts new pressure on Kaylie.

episodes.name: Lights, Camera, Retraction
episodes.overview: A surprise guest pulls Kaylie away from Pico Middle School. Can the Porcupines cover for their not-so-fearless leader? Elsewhere, Ray Ray goes rogue.

episodes.name: Cut It Out!
episodes.overview: The team's visit to Kaylie’s casita ends in humiliation for Jackie. Valeria dabbles in a new kind of witchcraft with a collection of homemade potions.

episodes.name: Wax On, Wax Off
episodes.overview: A double-booking dilemma leads to drama as the Porcupines’ wilderness cooking challenge falls on the same night as Kaylie’s big celebration.

1.name: Part 1
1.overview: After a brush with the law, teenage celebrity billionaire Kaylie Konrad is court-ordered to lead an inner-city wilderness club.

episodes.name: Winging It
episodes.overview: As a bird-watching adventure takes flight, Kaylie revamps her red carpet entrance. Meanwhile, Chewy attempts to woo Amber ... again.

episodes.name: Ship Out of Luck
episodes.overview: It’s sink or swim for the Porcupines when Kaylie organizes a “fishing trip” with a dash of disaster. Abandoned island getaway, anyone?

episodes.name: The Fundrager
episodes.overview: Kaylie and the gang get down to business for a team fundraiser. Amber, Ray Ray and Chewy plan a secret mission to connect with a celebrity guest.

episodes.name: Party Pooperazzi
episodes.overview: Love is in the air as Kaylie prepares for an extra-special first date. Elsewhere, Ray Ray takes Chewy's career to the next level.

episodes.name: Swing and a Mess
episodes.overview: Kaylie scores a new job as a flavored water spokesperson. Amber attempts to reclaim her secret wilderness spot -- and uncovers a major issue.

episodes.name: A Very Konrad Kristmas
episodes.overview: As the Porcupines prepare for a holly jolly celebration, Kaylie crashes with a special friend and learns how to have some humble holiday fun.

2.name: Part 2
2.overview: Ready for more glitz, glam and grit? Kaylie and the Porcupines sharpen their skills for a new slate of action-packed shenanigans.

episodes.name: An Ex to Grind
episodes.overview: As the Porcupines team up for a wilderness first aid competition, Kaylie spends more time with Colt … and his ex-girlfriend Margot.

episodes.name: The Old Witcheroo
episodes.overview: Valeria ditches her doom and gloom for a “good girl” transformation. Elsewhere, Kaylie tries to make a social media celebrity out of Colt.

episodes.name: 19 is the New 15
episodes.overview: It’s party time! Kaylie’s abuela pays a visit and recruits the Porcupines to plan Kaylie’s belated quinceañera — much to the dismay of Kit Konrad.

episodes.name: Pod Awful
episodes.overview: Jackie, Chewy and Kaylie dig deep for “Unexcused Absence,” their true crime podcast. Amber and Ray Ray compete for a chance at stardom.

episodes.name: Warlocks & Headlocks
episodes.overview: Ready to rumble? Ray Ray starts a celebrity feud after taking control of Kaylie’s social media. At school, Valeria encounters a not-so-secret admirer.

episodes.name: Fears of a Clown
episodes.overview: Silly fun takes a spooky turn as Kaylie hosts her first casita sleepover. But will the thrills and chills push one Porcupine to her breaking point?

episodes.name: Purr-fect Harmony
episodes.overview: Love (or something like it) is in the air as Ray Ray and Kaylie work to find Principal Dana a date. Elsewhere, Jackie struggles with her studies.

episodes.name: Crossing Wires
episodes.overview: On the heels of another Silver Pinecone loss, the team attempts to use Jackie's robot, Sal, as a secret weapon against the Los Feliz Frogs.

episodes.name: Bridge Over Troubled Daughter
episodes.overview: Kaylie fulfills her community service requirement — and considers a major move. Meanwhile, the Porcupines spring into action for a rescue mission.
